<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> die von Swangow, als ir uns vor
                                <expan>etliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>F<ex>ridrich</ex></expan> Zesels,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> mals schriftlich darauf
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        seid <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> gehabt, daz ir
                            <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>F<ex>ridrich</ex></expan> Zesel <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns niht genaigt wert; so
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wir von den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, wie ir villeiht
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Zesel
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns meynet <add>oder
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                            meynet</add> hilff zutun, <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex>,</expan> daz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>F<ex>ridrich</ex></expan> Zesel <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gesworn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ist und daz wir in
                            <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> seins burkrechts und bey uns zu
                                <expan>wone<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> ermant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, nach
                                <expan>auszweisu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> der abschrift
                                <expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan>. So <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        auch kein sache, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er in
                            <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>heit</expan> zu uns sprüch hab
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gehabe<ex>n</ex></expan> mug; hett er denn zu
                            <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> icht
                                <expan>zuspreche<ex>n</ex></expan> gehabt
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> noch hett, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im allweg <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        gleichs und rechts bey uns <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>zuhelff<ex>en</ex></expan>, als <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>, als ir an der
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>eingeslossen<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan> und an dem <expan>besigelte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vidim<ex>us</ex></expan>, daz <pb facs="#facs_213" id="105v"/>wir ewch vor
                            <expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>hörn</expan> geschikt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
                        habt. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> und getrawen wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>F<ex>ridrich</ex></expan> Zesels zu
                            <expan>entewsz<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und im kein hilff
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns noch <add>ander</add> die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zutun. Dewht ewch
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        von <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> Zesels <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu uns icht <expan>zuspreche<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        hettet und <add>uns</add> ungerechfertigt niht
                            <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> möchtet, so
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein vor dem <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        durchlewchtigisten fürsten und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sigmund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>e</ex>m</expan>, zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und zu
                        Beheim etc. kunig, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, da auch wir das
                            <expan>pillich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tun. Und dunkt uns, daz wir in den
                                <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> glimpf und rechts gnug
                                <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und pieten. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Thome <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
